    • 方法详细资料

      • select

        public static java.lang.String select(int[] CASNo)
        Get detailed information of specified reagent in database.
        参数:
        CASNo - CAS Number of reagent, three segments of number in array int[]
        返回:
        a compacted description of reagent. For example
        141-78-6:C4H8O2:ethyl acetate:88.11:500.0 g
        if such reagent is not recorded, would return
        No Such Record.

      • update

        public static java.lang.String update(java.lang.String descript)
        Add a reagent item to the database.
        参数:
        descript - a description string of the reagent. Each attribute should be separated by ":". For example
        141:78:6:C4H8O2:ethyl acetate:88.11:500.0
        返回:
        if database is updated successfully, would return
        Data Updated.
        if item with the same CAS Number already exists in database, return
        Already Exists.
        and the database would not be changed.

      • drop

        public static java.lang.String drop(int[] CASNo)
        Remove the record of specified reagent in database.
        参数:
        CASNo - CAS Number of reagent, three segments of number in array int[]
        返回:
        if the item is removed successfully, would return
        Data Removed.
        if the reagent is not recorded in database, return
        No Such Record.
        and the database would not be changed.

      • print

        public static java.lang.String print()
        Generate PDF file of reagents list according to the database. PDF could be visited at http://server_ip/PDF/list.pdf
        返回:
        would return
        PDF File Generatedif completed.
